btpd-el (1.7) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fixed torrent content extraction. Files in virtual directories are
    now alphabetically sorted.
  * Fixed file path parsing.
  * Better integration with Emacspeak.

 -- Igor B. Poretsky <poretsky@mlbox.ru>  Sun, 20 Jul 2014 10:14:30 +0400

btpd-el (1.6) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fixed treatment of compressed torrent files downloaded by clicking a
    link in w3m.
  * More consistent keymap definition for torrent view mode.
  * Main control panel revised. Active and inactive torrents are now
    placed in separate lists that can be individually shown or hidden.
  * Implemented navigation by sections in control panel using PGUP and
    PGDN keys.
  * Better integration with Emacspeak.

 -- Igor B. Poretsky <poretsky@mlbox.ru>  Sat, 24 May 2014 09:05:16 +0400

