  * The btpd-w3m module is left uncompiled to avoid dependency on the
    w3m package.
  * More appropriate dependencies.

 -- Igor B. Poretsky <poretsky@mlbox.ru>  Fri, 28 Jun 2013 15:22:57 +0400

btpd-el (1.4) unstable; urgency=low

  * More consistent keymap in the torrent view.
  * Implemented size calculation for selected items in the torrent view.
  * Fixed virtual directory structure construction.
  * After returning from a subdirectory in torrent view position is
    correctly restored.
  * Tracker URLs are included in torrent info.
  * Fixed interactive torrent adding.
  * Added keystroke to close a control panel.
  * More extensive description in README.Debian.

 -- Igor B. Poretsky <poretsky@mlbox.ru>  Wed, 12 Jun 2013 10:50:24 +0400

